<h2>Degree Requirements</h2>
<p>To earn a Bachelor of Science in Data Science with an Industrial Engineering Concentration from UIC, students need to complete university, college, and department degree requirements. The degree requirements are outlined below. Students should consult the <a href="/ucat/colleges-depts/engineering/">College of Engineering</a> section for additional degree requirements and college academic policies.</p>
